1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,405
택시 창밖으로 번지는 불빛
Lights blurring outside the taxi window.

2
00:00:07,405 --> 00:00:14,810
라디오에서 흘러나온 옛날 노래
An old song playing on the radio.

3
00:00:14,810 --> 00:00:22,214
이 시간엔 모든 게 느려져
Everything slows down at this hour.

4
00:00:22,214 --> 00:00:25,917
너한테 갈까 말까 고민만 해
I just keep wondering if I should go to you.

5
00:00:25,917 --> 00:00:29,620
편의점 앞 벤치에 앉아서
Sitting on a bench in front of the convenience store.

6
00:00:59,960 --> 00:01:03,399
따뜻한 캔 하나 손에 쥐고
Holding a warm can in my hand.

7
00:01:03,399 --> 00:01:08,560
네 연락을 기다리는 건 아닌데
It's not like I'm waiting for your call.

8
00:01:08,560 --> 00:01:13,959
자꾸 화면을 확인하게 돼
But I keep checking my screen.

9
00:01:13,959 --> 00:01:20,239
새벽 두 시 주파수가 맞는 밤
It's 2 AM, a night when our frequencies align.

10
00:01:20,239 --> 00:01:24,319
잡음 사이로 네 목소리가 들려
I hear your voice through the static.

11
00:01:47,760 --> 00:01:50,640
이 도시가 잠들면 우리만 깨어서
When this city falls asleep, only we are awake.

12
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:53,140
같은 하늘 아래 다른 곳에서
In different places, under the same sky.

13
00:01:53,140 --> 00:01:55,760
옥상에서 내려다본 골목길
The alleyway viewed from the rooftop.

14
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:58,640
가로등 하나가 깜빡이고 있어
A single streetlight is flickering.

15
00:01:58,640 --> 00:01:59,939
하고 싶은 말은 루프처럼 돌아
The words I want to say loop in my head.

16
00:01:59,939 --> 00:02:00,939
입 밖으론 한마디도 못 꺼내
But I can't utter a single word.

17
00:02:01,459 --> 00:02:03,859
이어폰 한쪽만 끼고 걸어
I walk with just one earbud in.

18
00:02:03,859 --> 00:02:06,599
네가 좋아하던 그 노래 틀어
Playing that song you used to like.

19
00:02:06,599 --> 00:02:08,860
발걸음이 리듬을 타는 밤
A night where my footsteps find a rhythm.

20
00:02:08,860 --> 00:02:13,240
혼자인데 혼자가 아닌 것 같아
I'm alone, but it doesn't feel like I am.

21
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:18,460
새벽 두 시 주파수가 맞는 밤
It's 2 AM, a night when our frequencies align.

22
00:02:18,460 --> 00:02:24,659
잡음 사이로 네 목소리가 들려
I hear your voice through the static.

23
00:02:24,659 --> 00:02:28,759
이 도시가 잠들면 우리만 깨어서
When this city falls asleep, only we are awake.

24
00:02:28,759 --> 00:02:29,280
같은 하늘 아래 다른 곳에서
In different places, under the same sky.

25
00:02:30,939 --> 00:02:34,240
전화할까 말까 세 번째 고민
Should I call or not? It's my third time wondering.

26
00:02:35,759 --> 00:02:39,580
나도 지금 네 번호 보고 있어
I'm also looking at your number right now.

27
00:02:40,099 --> 00:02:45,340
새벽 두 시 주파수가 맞는 밤
It's 2 AM, a night when our frequencies align.

28
00:02:45,340 --> 00:02:50,539
잡음 속에서 결국 너를 찾아
I finally find you amidst the static.

29
00:02:50,539 --> 00:02:56,900
이 도시가 잠들어도 우리는 깨어서
Even if this city falls asleep, we remain awake.

30
00:02:56,900 --> 00:02:59,259
같은 주파수로 이어져 있어
Connected by the same frequency.

